{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTTPS","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/https","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTTPS</strong> （安全的<em>HTTP</em>）是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP\">HTTP</a> 协议的加密版本。它通常使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/SSL\">SSL</a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/TLS\">TLS</a> 来加密客户端和服务器之间所有的通信。这安全的链接允许客户端与服务器安全地交换敏感的数据，例如网上银行或者在线商城等涉及金钱的操作。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基础知识","title":"基础知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>在维基百科上的 <a title=\"HTTPS\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTPS\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTTPS</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"HTTPS （安全的HTTP）是 HTTP 协议的加密版本。它通常使用 SSL 或者 TLS 来加密客户端和服务器之间所有的通信。这安全的链接允许客户端与服务器安全地交换敏感的数据，例如网上银行或者在线商城等涉及金钱的操作。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"HTTPS","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/https","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/https/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/https","title":"HTTPS"}],"pageTitle":"HTTPS - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}